HEADWORD: Piecener
<hw>Piece"ner</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
supplies rolls of wool to the slubbing machine in woolen
mills.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Same as <er>Piecer</er>, 2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Piecer</ent>⟦br⟧
